      <title>債券投資者為聯準會小幅寬鬆做好準備，選擇中間曲線道路</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/bracing-shallow-fed-easing-bond-investors-take-middle-curve-road-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[債券投資者選擇性地在投資組合中增加期限較長的債券，押注聯準會將推遲降息，並以比之前寬鬆週期更慢的速度降息，首先決定在本週的政策會議上維持利率不變。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/bracing-shallow-fed-easing-bond-investors-take-middle-curve-road-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:27:08 GMT</pubDate>
