      <title>安橋為其五大湖隧道工程選擇承包商</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/enbridge-selects-contractors-its-great-lakes-tunnel-project-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大能源公司 Enbridge 與 Barnard Construction Company, Inc. 和 Civil and Building North America, Inc. (CBNA) 維持了合資夥伴關係。該公司週二在一份聲明中表示，將建造麥基諾海峽的五大湖隧道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/enbridge-selects-contractors-its-great-lakes-tunnel-project-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
